text:
Goal: Beat the Game
Controls: wsad + mouse
You start from the beginning of the stage when you die

Make sure to pick up as many weapons as you can, youll need them.
Kills in the bottom right is the number of enemies you need to beat to open the exit of the level (its a blue portal thingy on the ground)
There are some breakable walls, they look like regular walls but with a huge crack in them. 
Warning: this game is LOUD, but for this type of game you need loud music so you might want to crank it up.
title: G U N N E L V I S I O N
